{"tid":46357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰鬥民族】沐浴露當酒飲 至少48人甲醇中毒死","createTime":"2016-12-19T15:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T02:12:22.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2055c4f213c43bfabb3e8321a3d890f012378270","tid":46357,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161219/large/1482153697_7275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161219%2Flarge%2F1482153697_7275.jpg&h=c0f83529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯西伯利亞伊爾庫茨克（Irkutsk）多名居民，將含有酒精的沐浴露當酒飲，未料沐浴露內含甲醇，至少48人中毒死亡。當地官員宣佈進入緊急狀態，並逐家逐戶上門查問是否有人不適，以免死亡人數進一步增加。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯傳媒《今日俄羅斯》引述調查人員表示，57人中毒被送院，部份人昏迷，受害人年齡介乎35至50歲，都是伊爾庫次克弱勢社群，當局已拘捕兩名涉嫌銷售沐浴露的人。<br />\n<br />\n調查人員表示，沐浴露包裝印有不可吞服的警告，但涉事居民未有理會，將它當作酒類飲用，經分析後證實沐浴露含有甲醇和防凍劑。而《今日俄羅斯》報道，沐浴露的招紙標示成份含乙醇、山楂提取物、檸檬油、甘油等等。<br />\n<br />\n調查人員及警方確定，當地逾100個地點有銷售這種沐浴露，並已沒收逾2000公升沐浴露。"},{"pid":"28f12723d6e470807e4f3f29019e995f4c8bce92","tid":46357,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底係邊邊錯<br />\n唔係班人當係酒噉飲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解要沒收晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec795572913f01f77073b3416cd0d26c0c0bf52b","tid":46357,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T22:44:29.000Z","msg":"消毒劑事小<br />\n<br />\n連坦克引擎防冷劑都照飲"},{"pid":"b5b82c3ec324cd5424d478a66bf807bf4ffd78f6","tid":46357,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"On9無極限<img src=\"/